29 Seconds of Farcaster ... What did you miss this weekend?

* The weekend started with a new FC Audio Chat app from @jc4p that everyone was testing, including Bert! @bertwurst.eth (I was there & heard a 'weenie whine'). We also got the Myanmar Blockchain Relief app thanks to @horsefacts.eth & @blockheim 

* Minimized mini apps is now a thing--which is useful for listening to a podcast or a chat while scrolling your feed. 

* Also, a new trending follow notification where if someone gets a lot of followers a notification goes out, particularly useful for new & growing accounts (s/o @woj )

* Our own @jrs , Asst Coach for the Florida Gators, is in the Final 4 & playing for the championship tonight & continues to take us BTS in San Antonio

* Speaking of the Final Four, March Madness has turned into $Bracky Madness revealing many of our psychotic tendencies in trading--s/o @tldr for elevating an already stressful experience

* @nounishprof & @adrienne will get you fully caught up--8:30 AM EST

new on warpcast: trending follow recommendations

the notification aims to solve 2 problems:
- new people should be able to build a quality audience faster
- existing users should be able to jump on new metas without spending hours on the app

we are very thoughful on how we send it: it only triggers once many people you follow, follow a new person in a short timespan

as always, you can turn it off in the notifications and shoot me any feedback ü§ù
